==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Setting-up exercise
<hw>Set`ting-up" ex"er*cise</hw>. <def>Any one of a series of gymnastic
exercises used, as in drilling recruits, for the purpose of giving an
erect carriage, supple muscles, and an easy control of the
limbs.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Settle</ent>⟦br⟧
